data.description: In the heart of Crafton Heights on the quiet street of Straka sits a beautiful house waiting for you to call it HOME! This adorable 3 bed/1 bath, 2-Story home. It boasts a great porch to relax on and large living room on the main floor which are several features that are sure to meet your checklist.  The bedrooms are bright with natural lighting and hardwood flooring throughout! The upstairs bath adorns a tiled bathroom that helps for easy cleaning! The property has a flat yard with an alleyway that works well for an extra off-street parking spot.  Located close to Downtown Pittsburgh, Shopping, Gyms, Restaurants and more! MUST SEE! Don't miss out!!
